name: I'm not your therapist but I'd like to cheer you up with my dorky art
description:
Piece #1 of the collection:
I'm not your therapist but I'd like to cheer you up with my dorky Art.

The series focuses on the fragility of the inner world and brings up topics that we often find in our long journey on earth. 

The inner world is made of thoughts, emotions, and feelings.
Sometimes is complicated to deal with them. With this collection, I want to share this world and all the positive and negative aspects.
